By utilizing our existing AI drug discovery workload for peptides, we can either agonize receptors to encourage growth of bones, muscle, and brain matter, or we can antagonize the loss of bones, muscle, and brain matter.

Below are our anticipated GPCR targets to agonize (activate):
Bone Density Loss: Parathyroid Hormone 1 Receptor
Muscle Atrophy: Ghrelin Receptor
Neurodegeneration: Glucagon-Like Peptide-1 Receptor

Below are our anticipated GPCR targets to antagonize (inhibit):
Bone Density Loss: Cannabinoid Receptor Type 1
Muscle Atrophy: Angiotensin II Type 1 Receptor
Neurodegeneration: Adenosine A2A Receptor

